 <br>
*Thanatos looked over the wound one more time, and then awaited Artemis's input.* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solariwolf@amazonsunite>solariwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Themiscryian War Queen</span><br>  Posts: 120<br> <font color=#993300>(3/14/03 2:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Examining</span><hr size=1> Solari looked to her aunt for some advice on this matter. <br>
 &quot;Artemis, do you have some insight on this? Why would a hydra be here? Have I done something to anger the gods?&quot; she asked softly. Solari was careful about asking her questions to Artemis...they were not that close, but Solari still held great admiration and respect for her aunt. She looked back at Megan and stroked her face gently, wishing she could take the pain away that she knew her daughter felt. <br>
 She then looked back to Thanatos. <br>
 &quot;You mentioned that you brought someone to the underworld who had this same mark? Where was this at?&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thanatosofdeath@amazonsunite>Thanatos of Death</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.joerghuber.com/images/art_c48.jpeg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#993300>(3/14/03 4:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> where it happened.</span><hr size=1> "I believe the man came from a small fishing town not to far away from amazon lands... I could get more information for you if you'd like. I've written down all the information about people's age, cause of death, and where they were from, since the beginning of time." <br>
 <br>
*Thanatos slipped his giant sythe behind his clock seeing that he probably would not need it at the present moment.* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=goddessartemis>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Virgin Huntress</span><br>  Posts: 446<br> <font color=#993300>(3/15/03 5:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/mogoddessartemis/images/triplemoon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: where it happened.</span><hr size=1> She looked from Thanatos, then to Solari and nodded.<br>
 &quot;Yes, it most definitly was a Hydra. I even think I might know which one it is. But I must find out if it was sent by anyone before I kill it. When I capture it, I will know all.&quot;<br>
Her eyes turned sad as looked down to Megan, she knew the girl had to be in a great deal of pain, but she looked up to Solari.<br>
<br>
&quot;Go to my temple and ask Dlasta for the wild water, she will know what I mean. Bring this back to Megan and cleanse her wound with it. It will kill any poisons and numb the pain as much as possible. Her life will not be in danger and she shall survive.&quot; <p>~ The Silver Goddess~&lt;br&gt;<br>
