 &quot;Alkaria, watch your sister....I shall return in a little bit. &quot; She said. She leaned down, kissed both her daughter's on the head, then turned to her company. &quot; Please, make yourselves at home.&quot;  <br>
 She then walked off the porch to find Dlasta.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thanatosofdeath@amazonsunite>Thanatos of Death</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.joerghuber.com/images/art_c48.jpeg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#993300>(3/17/03 4:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Waiting...But not for long.</span><hr size=1> *Thanatos senced that he would be needed again soon in another part of Greece.* <br>
 <br>
&quot;Artemis, excuse me but there is another soul that needs my taking at this time, I will return when the time is right.&quot; <br>
 <br>
*Thanatos went outside of the hut, where a dragon stood there wating for him. Thanatos claimed onto it and took off into the sky.* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solariwolf@amazonsunite>solariwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Themiscryian War Queen</span><br>  Posts: 135<br> <font color=#993300>(3/17/03 4:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Wild Water</span><hr size=1> Solari quickly did as Artemis had told her, retrieving the wild water from her temple and then heading back to her hut. She kept the worried thought from her head, keeping herself calm as she had always done, but this involved one of her own children. So worry to a point was allowed. <br>
 She ran up on the porch and saw that Thanatos had left. So she busied herself with cleaning her daughter's wounds with the water. Once that had been done, fresh bandages were placed around her arm, then Solari picked up her daughter and carried her inside to her bed. <br>
 Once making sure that Megan was comfortable, she offered dinner to Artemis.<br>
 &quot;You are more than welcomed to stay, Artemis. I have stew and herb tea. The bread will be done in a few more minutes.&quot; <br>
Solari said as she took down some bowls. &quot;Alkaria has been cooking this all day it seems.&quot; SHe looked to her daughter and smiled. &quot;So hopefully she didn't mess it up like the last one.&quot; <br>
<br>
 Solari teased her daughter lightly, hearing her laugh in the background.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=goddessartemis>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Virgin Huntress</span><br>  Posts: 447<br> <font color=#993300>(3/19/03 7:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/mogoddessartemis/images/triplemoon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wild Water</span><hr size=1> She watched Thanatos leave and Solari arrive back, she watched Solari cleanse the wound and knew the girl would be just fine.<br>
<br>
&quot;I would be deligted to stay for dinner Solari.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled, and looked around. &quot;If you need help with anyhting let me know.&quot; She had to chuckle slightly, she wasnt exactly the domestic goddess.<br>
